{"tid":1421713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉貼] 和理非c9的一段話","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:48:33.000Z","uid":262185,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f8daa049a8ebbc6f712c5c14a5dee0c00bd4e4","tid":1421713,"uid":262185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:44:25.000Z","msg":"幫auntie轉貼下，希望有更多方法幫到手<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n我住炮台山，是一名和理非 c9，昨天有去金鐘，宜家班黑警無人性，唔應該繼續流血被捕，唔可以俾佢哋咁興奮。遊行示威對正虎無損失，高層坐冷氣房，黑警打人發洩，成班都正仆街。所以要同佢地講經濟，宜家正虎最大經濟動力就係無謂基建，我哋要打擊正虎升降機天橋隧道經濟，十八區一齊阻止正虎興建呢啲無謂建設，等佢哋施政困難。我想到其中一個方法是申請法援，告政府行政失當。我已經有個 case，只是沒有無資產義士出面申請法援打官司。如果覺得呢個抗爭方法可行，請幫忙po 上連登，或者大家討論一下。謝謝。認真的，要做一些影響正虎施政嘅行動，勇武係時候休息一下。<br />\n/"},{"pid":"15e1c6b09e469ffb5fe4ac7ddd9081c08e9773e2","tid":1421713,"uid":253833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"和理非新回合<br />\n［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b5617ad79032d7667735734dc58e48aaa4db425","tid":1421713,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:46:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ba6acb29d7ac7c02cec30b8f88c5ee626b393005","tid":1421713,"uid":262185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:46:57.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a6daa764fa75b2ab4392cfbad60ac81b5eb55d69","tid":1421713,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"補圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7fgGzxi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7fgGzxi.png&h=8e2311d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3egOYY8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3egOYY8.png&h=38eace2d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}